  91:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** /**
  92:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief Configure the main internal regulator output voltage.
  93:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @param VoltageScaling specifies the regulator output voltage to achieve
  94:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         a tradeoff between performance and power consumption.
  95:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
  96:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref PWR_REGULATOR_VOLTAGE_SCALE1 Regulator voltage output range 1 mode,
  97:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                typical output voltage at 1.2 V,
  98:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                system frequency up to 64 MHz.
  99:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref PWR_REGULATOR_VOLTAGE_SCALE2 Regulator voltage output range 2 mode,
 100:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                typical output voltage at 1.0 V,
 101:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                system frequency up to 16 MHz.
 102:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  When moving from Range 1 to Range 2, the system frequency must be decreased to
 103:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        a value below 16 MHz before calling HAL_PWREx_ControlVoltageScaling() API.
 104:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        When moving from Range 2 to Range 1, the system frequency can be increased to
 105:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        a value up to 64 MHz after calling HAL_PWREx_ControlVoltageScaling() API.
 106:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  When moving from Range 2 to Range 1, the API waits for VOSF flag to be
 107:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        cleared before returning the status. If the flag is not cleared within
 108:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        50 microseconds, HAL_TIMEOUT status is reported.
 109:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL Status
 110:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   */
