 559:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  When APC bit is set, the I/O pull-up and pull-down configurations defined in
 560:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        PWR_PUCRx and PWR_PDCRx registers are applied in Standby and Shutdown modes.
 561:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  Pull-up set by PUy bit of PWR_PUCRx register is not activated if the corresponding
 562:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        PDy bit of PWR_PDCRx register is also set (pull-down configuration priority is higher).
 563:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        HAL_PWREx_EnableGPIOPullUp() and HAL_PWREx_EnableGPIOPullDown() API's ensure there
 564:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        is no conflict when setting PUy or PDy bit.
