1033:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** /**
1034:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief Enter Low-power Run mode
1035:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  In Low-power Run mode, all I/O pins keep the same state as in Run mode.
1036:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  When Regulator is set to PWR_LOWPOWERREGULATOR_ON, the user can optionally configure the
1037:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        Flash in power-down mode in setting the RUN_PD bit in FLASH_ACR register.
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Nathan\AppData\Local\Temp\ccfQQZVb.s 			page 114


1038:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        Additionally, the clock frequency must be reduced below 2 MHz.
1039:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        Setting RUN_PD in FLASH_ACR then appropriately reducing the clock frequency must
1040:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        be done before calling HAL_PWREx_EnableLowPowerRunMode() API.
1041:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @retval None
1042:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   */
